snippet.title: Little Cities: Bigger! | Launch Trailer | PS VR2
snippet.description:
Little Cities: Bigger!, the critically acclaimed VR city creator, is out now on PlayStation VR2, bringing cosy creativity and hours of fuss-free fun in its ultimate form.
